


The Application is fully functional.

All Forms are validated especially in creation or updation of event.

=> User cannot register again with same email address
=> User cannot add more than 3 events per day
=> user can only view its own events and can modify or delete them.
=> user cannot select previous date
=> User cannot select wrong time
=> Event End date must be greater than or equal to the start date.


The Application will show these above errors if the user will make any mistake any from the above.

The Frontend UI is user Friendly

